  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252920/extras/cd093f7db911ec212cbab9170aad74d3.webp?t=1738902643\" width=300 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Door Game Deluxe is a short, satirical RPG with simple top-down controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a door. Also, you have no idea where you are. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252920/extras/8540c3d48911edc4290371664baa0f27.webp?t=1738902643\" width=275 height=41 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New, original art & music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Endings featuring monotony and repetition! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arguably kind of funny! Sometimes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 3 deaths!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real 100% Stained Pine Wood!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to process the existential weight of waking up as a door! Alone! On an island!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's also free and only a few minutes long and you have no reason not to play it so go ahead and do that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252920/extras/cd093f7db911ec212cbab9170aad74d3.webp?t=1738902643\" width=300 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Door Game Deluxe is a short, satirical RPG with simple top-down controls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a door. Also, you have no idea where you are. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252920/extras/8540c3d48911edc4290371664baa0f27.webp?t=1738902643\" width=275 height=41 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New, original art & music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Endings featuring monotony and repetition! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arguably kind of funny! Sometimes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 3 deaths!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real 100% Stained Pine Wood!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to process the existential weight of waking up as a door! Alone! On an island!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's also free and only a few minutes long and you have no reason not to play it so go ahead and do that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
